 always an exponential or stretched exponential relaxation. Thus we\nconclude that the compressed exponential relaxation observed in experiments is\ndue to the out-of-equilibrium dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Jan 2011 17:59:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
