ation kernel is of Eynard-Mehta type, which\nhas appeared in two-matrix models and time-dependent matrix models studied in\nrandom matrix theory. Conformal covariance of correlation functions is\ndemonstrated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Jan 2011 11:51:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Jan 2011 06:24:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 9 Mar 2011 02:08:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-17"}
